explanation: This problem can be solved using dynamic programming. We create an array dp where dp[i] represents the minimum length of the string after removing the first i characters. We iterate over the string and for each character, we check if it can be removed with the previous character. If it can, we update dp[i] with the minimum length. If it cannot, we update dp[i] with the minimum length of the string without removing the current character.

